OL,3,CJersey beat Guernsey to move a step
OL,4,Ccloser to T20 World Cup
OL,6,FJersey Cricket have made it through to
OL,7,Fthe final qualifying stage for the T20
OL,8,FWorld Cup after victory over island
OL,9,Frivals Guernsey in Cyprus.
OL,11,FBoth teams had won all of their group
OL,12,Fgames to reach the final, but now only
OL,13,Fthe Jersey cricketers will continue
OL,14,Ftheir World Cup dreams after a four-
OL,15,Fwicket win.
OL,17,FGuernsey won the toss and batted first
OL,18,Fwith Josh Buttler's 50 guiding the
OL,19,FGreens to 139-5 at the end of their 20
OL,20,Fovers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
