PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779719232
OL,3,CJersey beat Guernsey to move a step
OL,4,Ccloser to T20 World Cup
OL,6,FZak Tribe was the pick of Jersey's
OL,7,Fbowlers, taking 2-10 off three overs,
OL,8,Fbut his work was only half done.
OL,10,FGuernsey's total felt slightly under
OL,11,Fpar, but their bowlers dragged them
OL,12,Fback into the game.
OL,14,FWhen Julius Sumerauer was bowled by
OL,15,FMatt Stokes without scoring, Jersey
OL,16,Fwere in trouble at 61-5.
OL,18,FHowever, the player of the match,
OL,19,FTribe, kept his nerve.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
