FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779719232
OL,3,CJersey beat Guernsey to move a step
OL,4,Ccloser to T20 World Cup
OL,6,FHis unbeaten 54 included five sixes
OL,7,Fand, ably assisted by Charlie Brennan
OL,8,Fand Ben Ward, saw his island home with
OL,9,Ftwo overs to spare.
OL,11,FJersey will now compete against Italy,
OL,12,FScotland, the Netherlands, and two
OL,13,Fother yet-to-be-decided nations for a
OL,14,Fspot at the 2028 T20 World Cup.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
